    "text": "\u2022 \"Harvard Business School Licensing Fee\" will be charged to business students (MBA, MS HRM, EMBA, MS Logistics & Supply Chain Management and MS Innovation & Entrepreneurship) @ Rs 22, 000/year. Payment of Student Fee 1. At the time of admission, students have to pay the admission processing fee, security, and full semester fee in advance. Dues are required to be paid on semester basis. 2. Invoice for admission charges along with first semester fee and Provisional Selection Letter will be available on NUST website. 3. Tuition fee will be payable on semester basis. Students must pay their fee in advance before the commencement of semester. 4. All students are responsible to keep record of the copies of paid invoices throughout their academic tenure. EMBA Students \u2022 Second week of the semester will be an add/drop period without any financial implications for the students. If the student drops a course",
